      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Quebec wrestling legend PCO makes his MEW in-ring debut! Stu Grayson returns to challenge Yayne Harrison for the MEW Championship! 7 wrestlers in a LADDER MATCH vying for the Kingmaker&#39;s Key, giving the winner a championship match whenever they choose! &quot;The Mountain&quot; Vanessa Kraven defends her MEW Women&#39;s Championship and much, much more!</p>\n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/nQEj2WiLVeQ?si=KrlUheRb4tr7MOV0' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>"
